headline: CARFAX Named Best Places to Work in Virginia for the 12th Time
summary: CARFAX earns the honor of being named one of the Best Places to Work by Virginia Business Magazine, marking its 12th win since the award's inception in 2011. This prestigious recognition is based on anonymous employee surveys that assess workplace experiences, policies, practices, and demographics. Virginia Business conducts the survey in partnership with the Best Companies Group.
